snippet.title: Blek - Official Game Trailer - iOS
snippet.description:
Blek by kunabi brother
Elegant game about imagination - Get it now.

Apple's App Store:
http://appstore.com/blek

Google Play:
http://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=kb.Blek

Amazon Appstore:
http://www.amazon.com/kunabi-brother-Blek/dp/B00LB9B5R6

• Best Mobile Game - Casual Connect Europe, Amsterdam
• Excellence in Innovation - International Mobile Gaming Awards
• Best Game - Content Award Vienna

http://blekgame.com
